  textVersion  =
  paste("Teng Gao, Ruslan Soldatov, Hirak Sarkar, Adam Kurkiewicz, Evan Biederstedt, Po-Ru Loh, Peter Kharchenko. Haplotype-enhanced inference of somatic copy number profiles from single-cell transcriptomes. bioRxiv 2022.")
